General.Name: Ctek AB
General.Description: CTEK AB (publ) provides battery charging products for all types of vehicles in Sweden, Nordics, DACH, the Americas, rest of Europe, and internationally. The company offers products ranging from 12V battery chargers, load balancing systems, and electric vehicle supply equipment, as well as back-end solutions. It serves in various industries, such as municipalities, energy companies, housing cooperatives, property owners, corporations, parking companies, and private individuals. The company was founded in 1997 and is based in Vikmanshyttan, Sweden.
